@node Introduction "Eraser: Introduction"

                                  Introduction
                                 --------------

   Eraser is a plugin for the famous Image-Manipulation-Program ArtEffect2+. As
   a normal PlugIn it integrates seamlessly in ArtEffect2+'s menu and waits
   happily for your attention.

   It is nothing impressive.
   It is written to help me in my daily work, and this is mostly the
   enhancement and correction of scanned, monochrome (or few-color)
   images.

   Eraser, does just what its name suggest, it erases the complete picture to
   the selected color.
   At least the part not covered by a mask (read stencil).

   It does very, very much the same than the eraser tool when hitting erase
   image. Still speed things up for me by sparing come mouseclicks.

@endnode

